{"tid":2033226,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"bno平咗權之後連登熱門繼續光時五缺","createTime":"2020-05-24T13:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:26:19.000Z","uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9266eda5a06bf3ee2ba6f03aefdbc2cab0b758","tid":2033226,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8552006d830d13062be2d1136690e581ebd99e","tid":2033226,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"de230bf40d45bdd61a471c6ad8d4d5f3ba41aa86","tid":2033226,"uid":358640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d9266eda5a06bf3ee2ba6f03aefdbc2cab0b758","tid":2033226,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}